- actor mailboxes are cancel-correct (two-phase)

## Core Requirements
- Actor trait + spawn API
- Mailbox built on two-phase channels
- Actor shutdown protocol integrates with cancellation:
  - stop accepting new messages
  - drain mailbox within budget
